    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and grate (don't chop!) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and grate (don't chop!) your <strong>ginger</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>meat-free chick'n</strong> into smaller, bite-sized pieces</p>",
