        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>sliced radishes</strong>,<strong> sliced cucumber </strong>and <strong>carrot ribbons </strong>in a bowl<strong> </strong>along with <strong>half </strong>of the <strong>Vietnamese-style marinade </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and give it a good mix up – this is your <strong>crunchy salad</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>remaining Vietnamese-style marinade </strong>and <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>meat-free chick'n</strong> to a bowl and mix to fully combine</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
