        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>meat-free chick'n</strong> along with any <strong>remaining Vietnamese-style marinade</strong> from the bowl and cook for 6-7 min or until warmed through and starting to brown – this is your <strong>Vietnamese-style meat-free chick'n</strong></p>",
