    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>sticky rice</strong> with the <strong>Vietnamese-style meat-free chick'n</strong> on top and the <strong>crunchy salad </strong>to the side</p><p>Sprinkle over your <strong>toasted sesame seeds</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>chopped mint</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
